@startuml Order Processing Saga - Delivery Request Failure
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Saga-хореография оформления заказа - Ошибка создания заявки на доставку

actor "Покупатель" as Customer
participant "Order Service" as Order
participant "Event Bus" as EventBus
participant "Inventory Service" as Inventory
participant "Payment Service" as Payment
participant "Payment Gateway" as PaymentGW
participant "Delivery Service" as Delivery
participant "External Delivery" as ExtDelivery
participant "Notification Service" as Notification
participant "Order History Service" as History

Customer -> Order: Оформить заказ
activate Order
Order -> Order: Создать заказ\n(статус: CREATED)
Order -> EventBus: Publish: OrderCreated
deactivate Order

EventBus -> Inventory: OrderCreated
activate Inventory
Inventory -> Inventory: Проверить наличие товаров
Inventory -> Inventory: Зарезервировать товары
Inventory -> EventBus: Publish: InventoryReserved
deactivate Inventory

EventBus -> Payment: InventoryReserved
activate Payment
Payment -> PaymentGW: Запрос на оплату
activate PaymentGW
PaymentGW --> Payment: Оплата успешна
deactivate PaymentGW
Payment -> Payment: Сохранить транзакцию
Payment -> EventBus: Publish: PaymentSucceeded
deactivate Payment

EventBus -> Delivery: PaymentSucceeded
activate Delivery
Delivery -> ExtDelivery: Создать заявку на доставку
activate ExtDelivery
ExtDelivery --> Delivery: Ошибка создания заявки\n(недоступная зона доставки)
deactivate ExtDelivery
Delivery -> EventBus: Publish: DeliveryRequestFailed
note right
  Причина: недоступная зона,
  неверный адрес,
  служба недоступна
end note
deactivate Delivery

EventBus -> Payment: DeliveryRequestFailed
activate Payment
Payment -> PaymentGW: Запрос на возврат средств
activate PaymentGW
PaymentGW --> Payment: Возврат выполнен
deactivate PaymentGW
Payment -> Payment: Сохранить транзакцию возврата
Payment -> EventBus: Publish: PaymentRefunded
deactivate Payment

EventBus -> Inventory: DeliveryRequestFailed
activate Inventory
Inventory -> Inventory: Освободить зарезервированные\nтовары
Inventory -> EventBus: Publish: InventoryReleased
deactivate Inventory

EventBus -> Order: DeliveryRequestFailed
activate Order
Order -> Order: Отменить заказ\n(статус: CANCELLED)
Order -> EventBus: Publish: OrderCancelled
deactivate Order

EventBus -> History: OrderCreated,\nInventoryReserved,\nPaymentSucceeded,\nDeliveryRequestFailed,\nPaymentRefunded,\nInventoryReleased,\nOrderCancelled
activate History
History -> History: Обновить историю заказа
History -> EventBus: Publish: OrderStatusUpdated\n(статус: CANCELLED)
deactivate History

EventBus -> Notification: OrderCancelled,\nPaymentRefunded
activate Notification
Notification ->> Customer: Отправить уведомление\n(заказ отменен:\nошибка доставки,\nсредства возвращены)
Notification -> EventBus: Publish: CustomerNotificationSent
deactivate Notification

Customer -> Order: Проверить статус заказа
activate Order
Order --> Customer: Статус: CANCELLED\nПричина: ошибка доставки\nСредства возвращены
deactivate Order

@enduml
